# 📋 Feedback App

live: https://voicy-rhwv.onrender.com/

This is a full-stack web application that allows users to:

- Register and log in
- Submit feedback/testimonials
- Like and dislike feedback from other users
- View all feedback publicly
- Navbar shows user name and dynamic auth links
- Uses Bootstrap for styling and Passport.js for authentication

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 User Authentication (Register/Login)
- ✍️ Authenticated users can submit feedback
- 👍 Like/👎 Dislike feedback with live counts
- 📃 View all feedback on the home page
- 👤 Logged-in user’s name shown in navbar
- 💡 Bootstrap UI for responsive design

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** EJS, Bootstrap
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB (Mongoose)
- **Authentication:** Passport.js (LocalStrategy)

